クラス UserSetting

public class UserSetting

Model for user-account data. (Related to one user account)

  • コンストラクタの詳細

    • UserSetting

      public UserSetting()
      Default constructor (default id is -1 and sex is other)

    • UserSetting

      public UserSetting​(String userId)
      Constructor Used when only the user-id is known, such as when selecting data.
      パラメータ:
      userId - Id of this user

    • UserSetting

      public UserSetting​(long id, String userId, String name, boolean nameFlag, String sex, boolean sexFlag, String birthday, boolean birthdayFlag, String area, boolean areaFlag, String specialty, String qualification, String pr)
      Constructor to set all items.
      パラメータ:
      id - Id of this user-setting
      userId - Id of this user
      name - The name of this user
      nameFlag - If this flag is true, then name is published on the publish-page.
      sex - Man, woman, etc.
      sexFlag - If this flag is true, then sex is published on the publish-page.
      birthday - Birthday of this user (used for calculation of age)
      birthdayFlag - If this flag is true, then birthday and age is published on the publish-page.
      area - Area of ??activity of this user
      areaFlag - If this flag is true, then area is published on the publish-page.
      specialty - This User's special skill
      qualification - Qualifications held by this user
      pr - Sales point of this user
